  • java.lang.Object
    • com.tomscz.afswinx.validation.AFValidatorPriority

  • public class AFValidatorPriority
extends java.lang.Object
    This class specify validators priority. It is used to better knowledge about priority and to visualize how validator is prior and how will be validation done.
